# Docs First

- If a decision changes architecture, scope, boundaries or implementation direction, update `MANIFEST.md` and the affected docs before or together with code.
- Keep repository truth in files, not only in chat.
- Use `docs/documentation-standard.md` when creating or revising substantial documents.
- Keep tasks represented in structured files under `tasks/` for substantial work.
